Package com.fasterxml.storemate.shared.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WithBytesCallback<T>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BufferRecycler
    Simple container class that can be used for efficient per-thread recycling of an individual byte buffer.
    BufferRecycler.Holder
    Simple container of actual recycled buffer instance
    ByteAggregator
    Helper class that is similar to ByteArrayOutputStream in usage, but bit more efficient for use cases StoreMate has.
    IOUtil  
    UTF8Encoder
    Helper class used for efficient encoding of JSON String values (including JSON field names) into Strings or UTF-8 byte arrays.
    UTF8UrlEncoder
    Convenience class for doing so-called "percent encoding" (and decoding), as defined by RFC-3986, see [http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3986.txt]).
    WithBytesAsArray
    Simple WithBytesCallback implementation to use when all you really want is a byte array copy.
    WithBytesAsContainer
    Simple WithBytesCallback implementation to use when you just want a ByteContainer as a result.
    WithBytesAsUTF8String
    Simple WithBytesCallback implementation to use when when you need contents to be converted to a UTF-8 String.
